                <h1><span>WaveMaker Swim School</span><span class="text-black"> - Learn to Swim with Certified Instructors</span></h1>
                <p>Small class sizes of no more than four for our youngest swimmers and six for our more advanced groups allows ample personal attention from one of Whitmore Lake Community Recreation's highly experienced instructors. Our instructors are Water Safety Instructor certified and/or Lifeguard certified through American Red Cross. Throughout the six class sessions we will focus on safety, gaining confidence, and improving technique. In addition to skilled instructors, our pool facility is perfectly designed to meet the needs of families and their children. One may choose to use one of our private family locker rooms or our spacious men's and women's locker rooms. Our pool offers a zero-depth entry ramp, stairs, and plenty of wall space to provide the best possible experience for your child. Finally, a brand new DE filtration and state of the art UV system keep our pool crystal clear and always safe. For more information, please email <a href="mailto:wlcrinfo@wlps.net" class="text-red text-decoration-underline">wlcrinfo@wlps.net</a></p>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <a href="https://wlcr.recdesk.com/Community/Program?category=8" target="_blank">
                        <button class="btn_normal mb-0">WaveMaker Swim School Registration</button>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
